    "description": "We at K Raheja Corp South Asia Partners are looking for an experienced Senior Property Advisor based out of Raipur. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout K Raheja Corp South Asia Partners:\nK Raheja Corp South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with K Raheja Corp South Asia Partners!",
